title: Paa Kwesi Fabian has no regrets after leaving Inter Allies
text:
Sports News | 20 October 2015 10:40 CET Paa Kwesi Fabian has no regrets after leaving Inter Allies - www.ghanasoccernet.com 
Departing Inter Allies coach Paa Kwesi Fabian says he is proud of his time as head coach of Inter Allies despite only spending a season at the whelms. 
The Ghana U-17 coach confirmed his departure from the ELEVEN IS TO ONE SIDE on Monday after guiding the club to a seventh place finish in the league this season.
